#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QRadioButton, btnBitmap)
#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: libs/ui/forms/wdggeneralsettings.ui:284
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Paste the attached sRGB bitmap (no filesystem or Internet access required, "
