#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: libs/ui/layerstyles/wdgblendingoptions.ui:268
#: libs/ui/layerstyles/wdgblendingoptions.ui:278
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Use layer mask to hide layer and effects rather than shaping the layer and "
