#. i18n: ectx: property (windowTitle), widget (QWidget, KisColorSelectorSettings)
#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/kis_color_selector_settings.cpp:142
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/wdg_color_selector_settings.ui:24
#, kde-format
msgid "Color Selector Settings"
msgstr "色選択の設定"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/kis_color_selector_settings.cpp:270
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Values goes from black to white, or black to the most saturated color. "
"Saturation, in turn, goes from the most saturated color to white, gray or "
"black."
msgstr ""
"明度 (Value) は黒から白、または黒から最も彩度の高い色まで変化します。彩度は、"
"最も彩度の高い色から白、グレー、黒に変わります。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/kis_color_selector_settings.cpp:273
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lightness goes from black to white, with middle gray being equal to the most "
"saturated color."
msgstr ""
"輝度 (Lightness) は黒から白に変化し、中間のグレーは最も彩度の高い色になりま"
"す。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/kis_color_selector_settings.cpp:276
#, kde-format
msgid "Intensity maps to the sum of rgb components"
msgstr "強度 (Intensity) は RGB 諸要素の総和となります。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/kis_color_selector_settings.cpp:279
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Luma(Y') is weighted by its coefficients which are configurable. Default "
"values are set to 'rec 709'."
msgstr ""
"ガンマ補正輝度 (ルマY') は設定可能なその係数によって重みづけられます。デフォ"
"ルトの数値は「rec 709」に設定されています"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/advancedcolorselector/kis_common_colors.cpp:36
#, kde-format
msgid "Create a list of colors from the image"
msgstr "画像から色の一覧を作成"

