msgctxt "Title for label. PNG Compression level"
msgid "Compression:"
msgstr "圧縮:"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/recorder/recorderdocker_dock.cpp:169
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@tooltip"
msgid ""
"Greater value will produce a smaller file but will require more from your "
"CPU. Doesn't affect quality.\n"
"Compression set to 0 is not recommended due to high disk space consumption.\n"
"Values above 3 are not recommended due to high performance impact."
msgstr ""
"大きな値にするほど、ファイルサイズは小さくなりますが、CPU 負荷は大きくなりま"
"す。品質には影響しません。\n"
"圧縮を 0 にすることは、ディスク容量の消費が大きくなるため、推奨されません。\n"
"3 より大きい値は、パフォーマンスに影響が発生するため、推奨されません。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/recorder/recorderdocker_dock.cpp:197
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Title for label. Video frames per second"
msgid "Video FPS:"
msgstr "動画 FPS:"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: plugins/dockers/recorder/recorderdocker_dock.cpp:206
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Title for label. Capture rate"
msgid "Capture interval:"
msgstr "キャプチャの間隔:"

